01:06.460 --> 01:07.700
It's my song.

01:09.360 --> 01:10.500
Kim Jenna...

01:15.200 --> 01:16.610
- This song...
- Do you...

01:16.710 --> 01:18.740
...know what you're saying?

01:23.880 --> 01:24.980
I'm sorry.

01:25.980 --> 01:26.950
But...

01:28.600 --> 01:31.150
It has a similar vibe to my song.

01:32.289 --> 01:33.660
How similar?

01:33.660 --> 01:34.259
I can't be sure...

01:34.259 --> 01:36.289
You just said it was your song.

01:36.289 --> 01:38.390
Then that means it's identical.

01:38.390 --> 01:41.060
No. It's not identical.

01:42.160 --> 01:44.729
I'm also flustered about why I said that.

01:44.729 --> 01:47.140
Give me your song. Let me listen to it.

01:48.470 --> 01:50.170
Your music video is awesome, right?

01:50.170 --> 01:52.009
We spent a lot of money.

01:54.680 --> 01:55.840
Jenna!

01:55.840 --> 01:58.110
Why are you here? You have a doppelganger?

01:58.979 --> 02:01.350
You're everywhere.

02:01.520 --> 02:02.680
What's going on?

02:05.550 --> 02:06.550
What?

02:07.190 --> 02:08.460
Did something happen?

02:08.720 --> 02:10.729
Why do you both look upset?

02:11.330 --> 02:12.760
What is it this time?

02:28.210 --> 02:29.579
Where are you?

02:29.950 --> 02:31.280
Should I go pick you up?

02:30.310 --> 02:32.510
CEO Park Seong-jin

02:31.780 --> 02:34.350
The gentlemen don't like to be kept waiting.

02:34.880 --> 02:37.220
You wore the dress I bought you, right?

03:00.610 --> 03:01.840
Don't go any further!

03:04.310 --> 03:05.310
You...

03:09.650 --> 03:11.090
Why are you here?

03:12.190 --> 03:14.090
I followed you from the study room.

03:14.090 --> 03:15.320
Are you crazy?

03:15.320 --> 03:16.320
Don't go.

03:16.960 --> 03:17.860
Stop.

03:17.860 --> 03:20.000
What do you care?

03:22.200 --> 03:23.170
Leave.

03:29.340 --> 03:30.840
We finished recording.

03:32.810 --> 03:34.710
So what?

03:37.079 --> 03:39.820
I left your part blank, so...

03:41.380 --> 03:44.020
You fill it. You fill it!

03:44.190 --> 03:45.190
Don't go inside!

03:45.390 --> 03:46.820
I'll do it!

03:46.820 --> 03:48.720
I'll make it happen!

